Android
====
Current projects in the directory:

SICalculator, an app that calculates simple interest after the user has specified a principal amount, interest rate, and year.

Smorgasbord, an app that serves as a collection of a few different activities:
-TextPlay has the user issue commands to manipulate the text view in simple ways.
-HateMail creates a hateful email message to send after the user provides input, mad libs style.
-Hangman has the user play hangman.
-CaesarCipher takes in a message provided by the user and encrypts or decrypts it according to the options set.
-Browser consists of a simple, Javascript disabled browser. Users can input a valid http or https url or a term that will automatically be searched on Bing to browse the Internet.
